================================================================================

Vendored from https://github.com/quickjs-ng/quickjs/archive/refs/tags/v0.14.0.tar.gz
(release 2025-04-11). Local layout: third_party/quickjs/{*.c,*.h}.

Excluded from upstream tarball:
- qjs.c, qjsc.c (CLI entrypoints — REPL and bytecode compiler)
- qjs-wasi-reactor.c (WASI mode)
- quickjs-libc.{c,h} (provides Os.exec / Os.read / Os.write / etc.;
  luban implements its own sandbox-friendly equivalent in
  src/qjs_engine.cpp)
- api-test.c, ctest.c, cxxtest.cc, fuzz.c, lre-test.c, run-test262.c
  (test programs)
- unicode_gen.c (build-time tool to regenerate unicode tables;
  luban uses the pre-generated headers)
- All .js runtime scripts (repl.js, standalone.js, amalgam.js); we do
  not embed the REPL or amalgamation tooling.
- meson / Makefile build files (luban uses CMake)

luban embeds QuickJS, not the standalone CLI.
